{"tid":1881390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"普通外科口罩都話呀 屌你老母 林鄭比成2萬個N95口罩同7萬件保護衣黑警托柒呀 班仆街賤狗連隔離營都唔敢入找童軍架喎","createTime":"2020-02-15T13:43:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T12:33:30.000Z","uid":252492,"like":80,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8a36a5f7e65d84304022a88abc02dba34ee1a16e","tid":1881390,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T13:43:47.000Z","msg":"醫護前線無N95 又無全身保護衣 原來去撚哂班毅進仔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上門查隔離病人有無走犯同入隔離營班毅進仔都淆哂底<br />\n走去找義工上門同找童軍入隔離營<br />\n要最高級防護裝備托鳩柒呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200215/GJCE533Z6OXSN4IHEE63VYBLIM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=telegram\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200215%2FGJCE533Z6OXSN4IHEE63VYBLIM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dtelegram&d=uD1rvIJwXfBqs1i1iclFx%2FS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=38b9ff16\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200215%2FGJCE533Z6OXSN4IHEE63VYBLIM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dtelegram&h=a234de5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200215/GJCE533Z6OXSN4IHEE63VYBLIM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=telegram</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警務處排名第二，獲發近64萬個。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">N95口罩方面，警方獲發數量更是眾部門之冠，竟然多達1.3萬個，而衞生署僅獲分配不足300個N95。</span></span>文件又披露各部門預計之後的物資使用量，其中警方更預期，2月至4月需要2.6萬件保護袍（Gown）、逾4萬件全身防護衣（Protective Coverall Suit）。"},{"pid":"8e61553f774f94cf75111c7332bd5af7a3d2687c","tid":1881390,"uid":252492,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T13:52:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7KBnTxg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=